content.rendered:
Directed by Pavan Sadineni

Written by Hussain Shah Kiran. Vasant Jurru. Pavan Sadineni. Rakendu Mouli

Star Rajendra Prasad. Naresh Agastya. Harsha Vardhan. Gnaneswari Kandregula. Satya Prakash. Rakendu Mouli. Ravi Josh. A. Jeevan Kumar. Pavani Reddy. Rocky

Language Telugu

Producers Vishnu Prasad. Sushmitha Konidela

Production Gold Box Entertainment
